Detailed Description

Board specific Dataflash commands header for the AT45DB642D as mounted on the USBKEY.

Note:
This file should not be included directly. It is automatically included as needed by the dataflash driver dispatch header located in MyUSB/Drivers/Board/Dataflash.h.
